# React Components

- **Style**: Functional components and hooks; no class components. Extract reusable logic into custom hooks in `src/hooks/`.
- **UI**: Ant Design for primitives; design tokens and shared styles in `src/styles/` (see `design-system.css`).
- **Editor**: Tiptap is used for rich text; follow existing Editor component patterns.
- **Testing**: Add or update unit tests when adding or changing components; use React Testing Library. UI changes that affect flows require E2E updates (see CONTRIBUTING.md).
